            </a>
            <a href="/docs" class="group inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to-indigo-600 text-white rounded-lg hover:from-blue-600 hover:to-indigo-700 transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl">
